**[#lightblue] ====Considerations
***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Data-Scalability.puml Scalability]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>Design for scalability to accommodate growing data volumes.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Data-Quality.puml Data Quality]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>Implement data validation and quality checks.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Data-Lineage.puml Data Lineage]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>Track the origin and transformation history of data.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Compliance.puml Compliance]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:16><color #black>Ensure data complies with legal and industry regulations **(e.g., [[GDPR.puml GDPR]], [[HIPAA.puml HIPAA]])**.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Data-Security.puml Data Security]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>Implement encryption, access controls, and data masking.

**[#lightblue] ====Best Practices
***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Data-Versioning.puml Data Versioning]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>**Maintain version control of data** and **[[data-pipeline/advanced-data-pipeline.puml pipelines]]**.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[Data-Documentation.puml Documentation]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>Document data schemas, transformations, and **[[data-pipeline/advanced-data-pipeline.puml pipelines]]** configurations.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[../../../3-devops/devops-plantuml-mindmap/Monitoring-and-Logging.puml Monitoring and Logging]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:14><color #black>Implement robust monitoring and logging to detect issues and performance bottlenecks.

***[#green] ====<size:14>**[[../../../3-devops/devops-plantuml-mindmap/Collaboration.puml Collaboration]]**
****[#orange] ====<size:16><color #black>Foster **collaboration** between **[[../11-key-areas-of-Data-Management-and-specific-data-roles/Data-Engineer.puml data engineers,]]** **[[../11-key-areas-of-Data-Management-and-specific-data-roles/Data-Scientist.puml data scientists,]] and** **[[../11-key-areas-of-Data-Management-and-specific-data-roles/Business-Analyst-vs-Data-Analyst.puml analysts.]]**

